you were overfilling opiates.

265
00:15:01,033 --> 00:15:03,502
Oh! It always flares
up when I get upset.

266
00:15:03,870 --> 00:15:06,738
Don't worry, Lucy.
We'll get you your meds.

267
00:15:14,380 --> 00:15:15,905
