272
00:15:29,328 --> 00:15:31,160
Fifteen-year-old girl
with Moebius syndrome.

273
00:15:31,230 --> 00:15:33,028
Your company denied coverage.

274
00:15:34,834 --> 00:15:36,393
No respiratory issues,

275
00:15:36,602 --> 00:15:38,662
