you wanna give this
little girl her smile.

280
00:15:46,679 --> 00:15:48,443
But if we paid for
everything wonderful,

281
00:15:48,514 --> 00:15:50,710
we'd go bankrupt. And
then who are we helping?

282
00:15:50,917 --> 00:15:53,682
We all know doctors cheat
diagnoses to get coverage.

283
00:15:53,786 --> 00:15:55,812
Deviated septum gets
you a free nose job.

284
00:15:55,888 --> 00:15:57,049
Migraine gets you botox.

285
00:15:57,123 --> 00:15:59,092
Do you really want
me to play that game?

286
00:16:00,460 --> 00:16:01,860
This isn't a game for me.

287
00:16:01,928 --> 00:16:04,557
We're a reputable company
with very high standards.

288
00:16:04,630 --> 00:16:07,725
Very high bonuses that get
even higher with your denial rate.

289
00:16:08,100 --> 00:16:11,180
I was gonna suggest we end this
before we say something we'll regret,

290
00:16:11,204 --> 00:16:12,763
but I believe that
just happened.

291
00:16:13,706 --> 00:16:15,868
Gretchen's socially
isolated, depressed,

292
00:16:15,942 --> 00:16:17,638
and that's only gonna get worse.

293
00:16:18,077 --> 00:16:20,389
What if she slashes her wrists?
You'd prefer to cover that?

294
00:16:20,413 --> 00:16:22,644
Are you threatening me
with a teenage girl's suicide?

295
00:16:22,715 --> 00:16:25,207
And God forbid something
does happen to her,

296
00:16:25,985 --> 00:16:27,429
'cause I'll make sure
that this conversation

297
00:16:27,453 --> 00:16:28,733
is part of the permanent record.

298
