Dr. Andrews said
smiles are contagious,

299
00:16:44,403 --> 00:16:46,599
and I'm testing that hypothesis.

300
00:16:47,640 --> 00:16:49,939
Well, I'm not sure your
study will prove anything.

301
00:16:50,009 --> 00:16:52,649
It might have something to do with
the lack of the Duchenne marker.

302
00:16:53,246 --> 00:16:54,475
Oh. Yes.

303
00:16:54,814 --> 00:16:56,339
But here you go.

304
00:16:59,418 --> 00:17:01,114
That wasn't a smile.

305
00:17:01,287 --> 00:17:02,778
Sure, it was.

306
00:17:05,791 --> 00:17:08,124
