myself in the perfect situation?

394
00:22:17,670 --> 00:22:22,335
You know, work, friends, future.

395
00:22:23,509 --> 00:22:25,603
Something I never
really had before.

396
00:22:27,646 --> 00:22:29,615
Maybe that's why
I screwed it up.

397
00:22:33,185 --> 00:22:35,848
You're not responding to
the antibiotics like we'd hoped,

398
00:22:37,456 --> 00:22:38,583
Lucy.

399
00:22:39,692 --> 00:22:40,785
You know, don't you?

400
00:22:42,962 --> 00:22:45,625
When the real Lucy Callard
showed up, it kind of gave you away.

401
00:22:48,167 --> 00:22:49,692
Is there anyone we can contact?

402
00:22:51,637 --> 00:22:53,333
Do you have any children?

403
00:22:53,939 --> 00:22:56,238
