405
00:22:59,278 --> 00:23:02,976
- Where is he?
- College, first one in our family.

406
00:23:04,049 --> 00:23:08,043
I had to choose between
premiums and tuition.

407
00:23:09,488 --> 00:23:11,957
Your son is very lucky to
have such a loving mother.

408
00:23:15,527 --> 00:23:17,155
I just wish you'd
got your antibiotics

